com.facebook.buck.android

Class ImmutableNdkCxxPlatform.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.android.ImmutableNdkCxxPlatform.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    ImmutableNdkCxxPlatform

    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class ImmutableNdkCxxPlatform.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of ImmutableNdkCxxPlatform. Initialized attributes and then invoke build() method to create immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread safe and generally should not be stored in field or collection, but used immediately to create instances.
